    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. It drives like a dream and is totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a fun weekend road trip, this beauty won't let you down. I've truly loved driving this car, and I'm sure you will too. Can't wait for you to come by and take it for a spin!",
