    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s chassis excellence. Under the hood, the S50 inline-six features a responsive single-VANOS system, delivering linear torque through a crisp ZF 5-speed manual transmission. Power is managed by a factory 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction through the apex. The suspension remains tight, benefiting from reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiastic use, the car features critical cooling system upgrades, including an aluminum radiator and high-flow water pump to mitigate heat-cycle fatigue. A true driver\u2019s spec, it offers the tactile feedback and analog engagement synonymous with the M-division's golden era.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
