    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes a perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic gray that retains a deep luster, though a close eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the lower front fascia and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the heated leather seats show minimal bolster wear and are free of any cracks or stains. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment system to the premium surround-sound audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the vehicle is in great shape, featuring a smooth-shifting automatic transmission and a quiet, responsive engine. It has a documented service history, including a recent cooling system flush and a fresh brake pad replacement just 2,000 miles ago. The tires have ample tread remaining, ensuring this car is ready for the road immediately with no hidden needs.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
