      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This automobile exhibits consistent performance and aesthetic integrity, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and reliability. With a documented history of care, this unit offers an exceptional balance of luxury and mechanical soundness. We invite you to experience the refined engineering and enduring value that define this exceptional offering.",
